                <note rend="inline" type="source">842.801/118: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Canada</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Robbins</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-02-19T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 19, 1935—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>13. Your despatch No. 1079, February 15. An instruction in reply must be delayed
                    pending further consideration as to the detailed effect of the proposal. The
                    speedy cooperation of other Departments is being obtained. You may reply to the
                    Prime Minister in this sense.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
